{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- and then we-- after they-- we'd been counted, the German, the-- the [NON-ENGLISH] will come with one small bread-- brown bread-- stale, and everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they give to the first person in the row that brick of brown bread-- stale and hard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were awaiting impatiently-- never mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it tasted the best food in the world, because we were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was-- she was given that piece, but it was already cut in five pieces.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So this little girl here, she has to take that piece and distribute to all the girls behind her in five pieces.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was-- call it, like maybe 100 grams of bread for the whole 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That, it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, there was a little bit of soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The little bit of soap would consist, you know, like some cabbages, and potatoes with the skin, and the-- and the-- and the rubbish-- all inside without being wash.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, you know, they were going to give us a [NON-ENGLISH], which it means a little container to each one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Many times, you know, we-- we can't even eat that soup, because it was finish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because we were-- you know, as I say, we were from the Mediterranean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We didn't know how to speak the language.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We didn't know German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were always the last to get whatever it was being distributed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were happy-- we were lucky that we were with my sister at the time-- and my other sister-- the three sisters.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we made a plan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because many girls, they were on their own.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They will take the bread, 100 grams, just a piece of bread like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They will eat the bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
